        "original": "遠い君の記憶",
        "english": "Your distant memory",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:35.400",
        "end": "01:43.200",
        "original": "(どこか懐かしいだれかと出会う度に、頭に浮かぶ映像が鮮明になってくる)",
        "english": "(Every time I meet someone nostalgic, the images that come to mind become clearer)",
