        "type": "on_screen_text"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:43.400",
        "end": "01:48.800",
        "original": "(もう少しで……何かがわかりそうな気がした)",
        "english": "(I felt like I was close to understanding something...)",
        "alignment_source": "visual_inference",
        "type": "on_screen_text"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:49.600",
        "end": "01:52.300",
        "original": "それって、ライブなんじゃないかな？",
        "english": "Isn't that... a live performance?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:52.600",
        "end": "01:53.300",
        "original": "ライブ？",
        "english": "Live?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:53.750",
        "end": "01:56.350",
        "original": "うん。そう、私、旅芸人だから噂で聞いたことがあるんだけど",
        "english": "Yeah. As a traveling entertainer, I've heard rumors about it.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:56.550",
        "end": "02:04.200",
        "original": "「オンガク」があった頃には、よく開催されてたんだって",
        "english": "They say they were held often back when 'Music' existed.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:06.400",
        "end": "02:12.000",
        "original": "(そうだ、あたしはライブをやっていたんだ…)",
        "english": "(That's right, I was doing live performances...)",
        "alignment_source": "visual_inference",
        "type": "on_screen_text"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:12.450",
        "end": "02:17.400",
        "original": "ねえ、気になるなら今からここで私といっしょにやってみる？",
        "english": "Hey, if you're curious, do you want to try it here with me now?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:17.700",
        "end": "02:18.400",
        "original": "え？",
        "english": "Eh?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:18.750",
        "end": "02:22.300",
        "original": "ていうかやろうよ！ あなたとならやってみたい！",
        "english": "I mean, let's do it! I want to try it with you!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:22.400",
        "end": "02:26.300",
        "original": "「ライブ」ってやつを！",
        "english": "A 'live performance'!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:30.850",
        "end": "02:36.150",
        "original": "遠くで聞こえる",
        "english": "I hear it from afar",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:36.650",
        "end": "02:42.250",
        "original": "わたしを呼ぶ声",
        "english": "The voice calling me",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:42.500",
        "end": "02:47.250",
        "original": "あなたの涙の",
        "english": "The reason for your tears",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:47.600",
        "end": "02:53.200",
        "original": "理由を知ってたはずなのに",
        "english": "I should have known why",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:54.050",
        "end": "02:56.650",
        "original": "乾く前に",
        "english": "Before they dry",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:56.800",
        "end": "02:59.450",
        "original": "枯れる前に",
        "english": "Before they wither",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:59.600",
        "end": "03:06.100",
        "original": "全て捧げようと",
        "english": "Wishing to offer everything",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:06.500",
        "end": "03:10.500",
        "original": "あなたにだけ",
        "english": "Only to you",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:18.200",
        "end": "03:23.400",
        "original": "なにを求めるのか 誰を愛するのかさえ",
        "english": "What to seek, even whom to love",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:23.650",
        "end": "03:28.450",
        "original": "わからず",
        "english": "Without knowing",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:29.100",
        "end": "03:33.400",
        "original": "灰のように朽ちていく心に",
        "english": "In a heart decaying like ash",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:33.600",
